(1&2)
Kissena B??, south of Peck Ave., showing in a set of two views an old house belonging to Jake Schleider Snr. in 1896, just north of Mill Creek. This property is midway between North Hampstead Turnpike and Peck Ave. (formerly West Ave.) This is a set of two views.
January 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

(3)
The same, at a later date, showing a further view northward to Rose Ave.
March 3, 1937.
P.L. Sperr
